# IntelliJ HTTP Client examples for technical-interview-demo
# User profile requests require an authenticated session. Updates also require CSRF.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@sessionCookie = paste-technical-interview-demo-session-here
@csrfToken = paste-x-csrf-token-here

### UserProfileController - current authenticated user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
Accept: application/json

### UserProfileController - update preferred language (authenticated + CSRF)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/preferred-language
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "preferredLanguage": "pl"
}
